{"tid":2074672,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"新歌: 我們都是熱血長大的","createTime":"2020-06-22T09:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T11:39:38.000Z","uid":8968,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a3833b5c6ae2f44387a493235b8c2afb5dad8e","tid":2074672,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:29:19.000Z","msg":"連綿雨 錦滿也浸沒了<br />\n寒澈骨 落屎渠變黃掉<br />\n捱下了 才發現POLY上<br />\n遍山差狗了<br />\n<br />\n立法了 松泰放肆地笑<br />\n才會懂 立會盡量忘掉<br />\n而投票這刻 才發現極渺小<br />\n學會放棄了<br />\n<br />\n熱血有著熱血畏懼 熱血都有熱血唏噓<br />\n年年參選年年敗去 而泰博是沈著面對<br />\n陳云老矣 說故事如傻孩渴睡<br />\n可說艱苦的熱時 怎會了無生趣<br />\n人群裡為洋達顧慮 逃離洋達逃離空虛<br />\n時而走近時而遠去 熱散與聚 都居於心裡<br />\n立會漂泊在松泰驀然回首<br />\n熱血還是不對<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97b60fda52b4e2fd065112fda1697861c68c254","tid":2074672,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"冇句啱音 u are fired<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0ad0f9c5d75b05b0f24a1a3e7efdcd8be54a69","tid":2074672,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f97b60fda52b4e2fd065112fda1697861c68c254","tid":2074672,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"冇句啱音 u are fired<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁岩音"},{"pid":"8c834e6116f6de814585b5802ede305193989f24","tid":2074672,"uid":33730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:35:59.000Z","msg":"年年參選年年敗去 而泰博是沈著面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7b83a7a738ad1ee973e0dbb530aba606c858fe","tid":2074672,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c834e6116f6de814585b5802ede305193989f24","tid":2074672,"uid":3373